 \displaystyle\lim_{(h,k) \to(0,0)}{\frac{\left |{hk}\right |}{\left |{(h,k)}\right |}}=0
h^2\leq h^2+k^2\Rightarrow \left |{h}\right |=\sqrt {h^2}\leq \sqrt {h^2+k^2}=\left |{(h,k)}\right |\Rightarrow \frac{1}{\left |{(h,k)}\right |}\leq \frac{1}{\left |{h}\right |} (*)
\left |{hk}\right |
\frac{\left |{hk}\right |}{\sqrt {h^2+k^2}}\leq \frac{\left |{hk}\right |}{\left |{h}\right |}=\left |{k}\right |
\displaystyle\lim_{(h,k) \to(0,0)}{\frac{\left |{hk}\right |}{\sqrt {h^2+k^2}}}\leq \lim_{(h,k) \to(0,0)}{\left |{k}\right |}=0
 \displaystyle\lim_{(h,k) \to(0,0)}{\frac{\left |{hk}\right |}{\left |{(h,k)}\right |}}=0
